# _local/ is internal working material and is NOT part of the published library:
# the 2026-07-10 audit package, the initial-discovery design docs and strategy
# briefs, and session logs. It is deliberately untracked.
#
# This was not always true. Until 2026-07-12 the library itself lived under
# _local/templates/ and this file re-included the directory against the user's
# global `_LOCAL/` ignore rule so the work could be version-controlled while the
# final scaffold stayed an open question. Decision HY-2 (scaffold graduation)
# closed that question: the product now lives at templates/, tools/, and atlas/,
# so _local/ finally means what its name says.
# See docs/decisions/20260712-scaffold-graduation-flat-templates.md
_local/

# Tool caches and OS junk.
.memsearch/
**/.impeccable/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# subagent-driven-development scratch ledger
.superpowers/
